            </div>
          </div>
          <div class="tool-card-foot">
            <div class="tool-best-for"><strong>Best for:</strong> Operators who want traffic, not a keyword spreadsheet.</div>
            <a href="/checkout/" class="tool-cta-btn">Start at $99/mo →</a>
